Package mdfs.utils

Class Summary
ArrayUtils Usefull tools when dealing with Arrays.
Config A class that statically enables access and query the config file mdfs/config/config.cfg for data
FSTree<E> A implementation of a file structure that enable one to store generic nodes with a String key The String key should be the path the node is stored at.
Hashing A simple implementation allowing hashing if String to MD5 or SHA-1
SplayTree<Key extends Comparable<Key>,E> Top-Down Splay Tree implementation (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Splay_tree).
Time Simple way of getting timestamps in the form of yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss
Verbose Simple class that in a Structured way of printing text
